items.title: MSTech In Lebanon
items.text: Aims to provide planning, consultancy, project management and installation of mechanical systems that is not only technically and efficient but also aligns with the owner's vision, optimizes space, promotes economic efficiency, incorporates sustainable practices, and integrates well with the architectural design..

items.title: MSTech In Germany
items.text: Aims to provide planning, consultancy and project management of mechanical systems for residential building, office buildings, and hotels throughout Germany.
